+-------+-----------------------+--------+------+-----+-----+-------+--------------+
|       | Item Monetary Values                                                     |
+-------+-----------------------+--------+------+-----+-----+-------+--------------+
|       | $07A650 - $07A74F : 1 Byte Each / 256 Bytes                              |
+-------+-----------------------+--------+------+-----+-----+-------+--------------+
|       | 'PSUDOCODE FOR DETERMINING COST                           | < THIS       |
|       |                                                           | HOLDS FOR    |
|       |                                                           | ANYWHERE GP  |
|       |                                                           | IS           |
+-------+-----------------------+--------+------+-----+-----+-------+--------------+
|       | IF (HEX) < 0x79 THEN                                      | CALCULATED*! |
+-------+-----------------------+--------+------+-----+-----+-------+--------------+
|       | 'Math EQ1                                                 |              |
+-------+-----------------------+--------+------+-----+-----+-------+--------------+
|       | COST = ConvertToDecimal(HEX) * 10                         | * But not    |
|       |                                                           | all GP!      |
+-------+-----------------------+--------+------+-----+-----+-------+--------------+
|       | ELSE IF> (HEX) > 0x80  COLOR="blue">THEN                  |              |
+-------+-----------------------+--------+------+-----+-----+-------+--------------+
|       | 'Math EQ2                                                 |              |
+-------+-----------------------+--------+------+-----+-----+-------+--------------+
|       | COST = ( ConvertToDecimal(HEX) - 128 ) * 1000             |              |
+-------+-----------------------+--------+------+-----+-----+-------+--------------+
|       | END IF                                                    |              |
+-------+-----------------------+--------+------+-----+-----+-------+--------------+
| INDEX | ITEM NAME (UNIV)      | $ADDR. | 0x00 | DEC | EQN | VALUE | SELL         |
|       |                       |        |      |     |     | (BUY) |              |

| 4D  |           | Summon   | Goblin      | Goblin Appears         |   When these   |
|     |           | Spell    | Punch       |                        | bytecodes are  |
|     |           |          |             |                        | used on items  |
|     |           |          |             |                        |  as the spell  |
|     |           |          |             |                        |  cast effect   |
|     |           |          |             |                        |    it get's    |
|     |           |          |             |                        | interesting... |
|     |           |          |             |                        |  The party is  |
|     |           |          |             |                        |  replaced by   |
|     |           |          |             |                        |   the summon   |
|     |           |          |             |                        |  graphic and   |
|     |           |          |             |                        | it stays that  |
|     |           |          |             |                        |  way for the   |
|     |           |          |             |                        |  duration of   |
|     |           |          |             |                        |  the battle.   |
|     |           |          |             |                        | The party can  |
|     |           |          |             |                        |  continue to   |
|     |           |          |             |                        |  function as   |
|     |           |          |             |                        |    normal,     |
|     |           |          |             |                        |   however it   |
|     |           |          |             |                        |   seems they   |
|     |           |          |             |                        | can't be hit!  |
|     |           |          |             |                        |   If you use   |
|     |           |          |             |                        |    the item    |
|     |           |          |             |                        |   again the    |
|     |           |          |             |                        |  summon will   |
|     |           |          |             |                        |   re-attack!   |
|     |           |          |             |                        |    It's An     |
|     |           |          |             |                        |  interesting   |
|     |           |          |             |                        | thing to play  |
|     |           |          |             |                        |     with!!     |
